HEADWORD: Jeniquen
<hw>Je*ni"quen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.
<ets>jeniquen</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A Mexican name for
the Sisal hemp (<spn>Agave rigida</spn>, <it>var.</it>
<var>Sisalana</var>); also, its fiber.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>hen⟦imac⟧equen</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jenite</ent>⟦br⟧
